<div>
  <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center">
    <div class="sm:flex-auto">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">unu VIN Decoder</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Decode your scooter's Vehicle Identification Number.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8">
  
  <% if flash[:error] %>
    <div class="rounded-md bg-red-50 p-4 mb-4" role="alert">
      <%= flash[:error] %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <% if flash[:community_help] %>
    <div class="rounded-md bg-indigo-50 p-4 mb-4" role="alert">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2"><%= flash[:community_help][:title] %></h3>
          <p class="text-sm"><%= flash[:community_help][:message] %></p>
        </div>
        <a href="<%= flash[:community_help][:link] %>" 
           target="_blank" 
           class="ml-4 btn-primary">
          <%= flash[:community_help][:link_text] %>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <!-- Grid layout for desktop -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <!-- VIN Input Form - narrower on desktop -->
    <div>
      <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <label for="vin-input" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">
            Enter Vehicle Identification Number (VIN)
          </label>
          <input type="text" 
                id="vin-input" 
                placeholder="e.g. WUNU2S3A6KZ000001" 
                required
                maxlength="17"
                class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline">
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs italic mt-2">
            VIN must be 17 characters long and start with WUN. Try it out with WUNU2S3A6KZ000001.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <button type="button" 
                  onclick="decodeVin()" 
                  class="btn-primary">
            Decode VIN
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <script>
        function decodeVin() {
          const vin = document.getElementById('vin-input').value.trim().toUpperCase();
          if (vin && vin.length === 17 && vin.startsWith('WUN')) {
            window.location.href = '/vin-decoder/' + vin;
          } else {
            alert('Please enter a valid 17-character VIN starting with WUN');
          }
        }
        
        // Also allow pressing Enter to submit
        document.getElementById('vin-input').addEventListener('keypress', function(e) {
          if (e.key === 'Enter') {
            decodeVin();
          }
        });
      </script>
    </div>

    <!-- What is a VIN box - flows next to input on desktop -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">What is a VIN?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        A Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) is a unique 17-character code used to identify 
        individual motor vehicles. For unu scooters, the VIN provides details about the 
        model, year of manufacture, and other specific information.
      </p>
      
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">unu Scooter 2.x VIN Format</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
        The unu Scooter 2.x VIN follows this format:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-md mb-3 text-sm">
        <code class="font-mono">WUN U2S <span class="text-indigo-600">X</span><span class="text-green-600">Y</span> <span class="text-amber-600">C</span> <span class="text-red-600">Z</span> <span class="text-purple-600">P</span> NNNNNN</code>
      </div>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600">X</span>: Motor power (2 = 2kW, 3 = 3kW, 4 = 4kW)</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-600">Y</span>: Version (A = max 25 km/h, B = max 45 km/h)</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-amber-600">C</span>: Check digit</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-red-600">Z</span>: Year of manufacture (K = 2019, L = 2020, M = 2021, etc.)</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">P</span>: Manufacturing plant (Z = Zhuhai, China)</li>
        <li>NNNNNN: Serial number</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic">
        Example: WUNU2S4BXM<span class="text-gray-400">Z000123</span> = 4kW motor, max 45 km/h, built in 2021
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
